bDBaR1EyYVRkTVEyaHNNa1pZZDJKbVUxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "First time here, good impression 👍 so fancy in there 🤩 very clean bathroom and super friendly staff.  Had a black tea milk with oat milk 🥛 loved it! They give it to you in a fancy bag which I had never seen before.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First time here, good impression 👍 so fancy in there 🤩 very clean bathroom and super friendly staff.  Had a black tea milk with oat milk 🥛 loved it! They give it to you in a fancy bag which I had never seen before.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anais", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107482979338289587296/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHhM6VyyQSJ559FISNFSeTfa4BpeJ9ixK6JZsysqodFQWc5qjb=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-23T04:47:10.855788696Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kd2RubDBaR1EyYVRkTVEyaHNNa1pZZDJKbVUxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kd2RubDBaR1EyYVRkTVEyaHNNa1pZZDJKbVUxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c1b2991fb735:0xa3a6d9c9e0c1044c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNbcfmbLBwoARTATB4MnZpqM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoRldVeHJiVnAzYnpSc1MyOURTa0oxTVZGeU5WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "During their grand opening, I ordered a Roasted Black Tea Latte, which tasted watered down with milk and didn’t have much flavor. It was over $8 with tax and wasn’t really worth the money. Very disappointed!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "During their grand opening, I ordered a Roasted Black Tea Latte, which tasted watered down with milk and didn’t have much flavor. It was over $8 with tax and wasn’t really worth the money. Very disappointed!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cc", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106593424780215352285/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0BykzuDX-_4CfX-z3s_58NmUzWudkAjvLPzo93pjQkcd4Aqs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-25T15:51:58.715250628Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoRldVeHJiVnAzYnpSc1MyOURTa0oxTVZGeU5WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoRldVeHJiVnAzYnpSc1MyOURTa0oxTVZGeU5WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c1b2991fb735:0xa3a6d9c9e0c1044c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNbcfmbLBwoARTATB4MnZpqM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xnMGIzSlZNV3RmUmxaMVV6TkdabHBhVlRoSldXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "New tea spot (no boba) with some kind of foreign notoriety. Idk.  Stopped by at 330 on a Friday, no line. The tea drinks here actually taste like tea.  That certainly not the case at any boba tea spot.  Super bougie packaging and prices to go with it.  Not a serious place for tea but better than a boba tea for sure.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "New tea spot (no boba) with some kind of foreign notoriety. Idk.  Stopped by at 330 on a Friday, no line. The tea drinks here actually taste like tea.  That certainly not the case at any boba tea spot.  Super bougie packaging and prices to go with it.  Not a serious place for tea but better than a boba tea for sure.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Realcelebetweets", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103096453549219536637/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-lLyGe7x6JfeU30GIaWlqt4Qf1mcViTQW6c-m2fIxckuv5yU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T01:23:32.666356836Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xnMGIzSlZNV3RmUmxaMVV6TkdabHBhVlRoSldXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xnMGIzSlZNV3RmUmxaMVV6TkdabHBhVlRoSldXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c1b2991fb735:0xa3a6d9c9e0c1044c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJNbcfmbLBwoARTATB4MnZpqM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xclltTnFZa3R6Tkc1NFMyaFViVkpHZEZrMVdsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Chagee is a premium tea brand from china with high quality tea, was super excited for the soft opening today! Location is at the Americana, lovely stroll through the outdoor mall (right next to Tumi). Staff is friendly, app is easy to use. Decently spacious for the size with AC and WiFi. Every drink I’ve tried from them is exceptional. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Chagee is a premium tea brand from china with high quality tea, was super excited for the soft opening today! Location is at the Americana, lovely stroll through the outdoor mall (right next to Tumi). Staff is friendly, app is easy to use. Decently spacious for the size with AC and WiFi. Every drink I’ve tried from them is exceptional. Highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ying Liang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116730976160866129316/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRKgOGqtEKPpkTo8PoD9Op8tt3BnwKi8cEpUlvc4wsWAWGxug1=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-27T21:31:59.399597373Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xclltTnFZa3R6Tkc1NFMyaFViVkpHZEZrMVdsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xclltTnFZa3R6Tkc1NFMyaFViVkpHZEZrMVdsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c1b2991fb735:0xa3a6d9c9e0c1044c"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJNbcfmbLBwoARTATB4MnZpqM/photos/AWCwydiNPbcqQrZeL2W6_y7fTFDwM